pullrequest.title: Renamed MPL joints and links to be consistent with APL names

content.raw:
The names in the current mpl file are those that APL gave us. I don't think we should change them back to an older version.

Clarification: I'm assuming Emo will be using the newer names as well. We might want to avoid confusion among the teams.
